             was indicted for <rs id="t18200412-178-off1032" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18200412-178-off1032" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18200412-178-off1032" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18200412-178-cd1033" type="crimeDate">19th of April</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18200412-178-off1032 t18200412-178-cd1033"></join>, one watch, value 10 l.; two seals, value 2 l., and one watch key, value 5 s.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               <persName id="t18200412-178-victim1774" type="victimName">
                  James 
                  M'Donald
               <interp inst="t18200412-178-victim1774" type="surname" value="M'Donald"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18200412-178-victim1774" type="given" value="James"></interp>
